{"tid":2419697,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[好爸爸]躁父不忿女兒每天被校園欺凌　怒闖課室刺殺9歲童判死刑︰我不後悔","createTime":"2021-02-23T12:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T15:48:26.000Z","uid":105567,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"48a04c242beb5d2cc88cab416c0390de155d2d42","tid":2419697,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T12:32:02.000Z","msg":"校園欺凌者成為刀下亡魂。內地江西一名爸爸因其三年級女兒遭同班男同學長期欺凌，竟持刀衝入教室，狂刺女兒的9歲同班男同學10多刀致當場身亡，事後該名爸爸被判處死刑，還聲言「不後悔」，不會上訴，至上月28日伏法。<br />\n綜合內地傳媒報道，來自江西省上饒市的王姓爸爸，女兒就讀當地的上饒市第五小學，當時三年班的女兒於2019年5月9日放學回家時向爸爸訴苦，稱自己被同班的劉姓男同學欺負，於是王爸爸就在微信的家長群組表達不滿，揚言會在校外等男童放學。<br />\n<br />\n當時有網民公開一段對話截圖，指在對話中的「何紫璇爸爸」，就是行兇的王父。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2884405/?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2884405%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv322%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=b26b7510\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2884405/?r=mcsdfb</a>"},{"pid":"9f3cfeb3b63d90b5f162b781b144e6f6ee4711d2","tid":2419697,"uid":39459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T12:33:38.000Z","msg":"一次死兩件，大善"},{"pid":"bb534506961687929bffbaaeb2b58f6f79467eb8","tid":2419697,"uid":188334,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"爸爸姓王，個女姓何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3f39758803ed8de0cf5949bde9ed71c9611700","tid":2419697,"uid":326140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb534506961687929bffbaaeb2b58f6f79467eb8","tid":2419697,"uid":188334,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"爸爸姓王，個女姓何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T12:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380bb92fb6ac315f3bf4c5e7031af9e5ff7fe776","tid":2419697,"uid":165361,"like":1,"dislike":0